text: Tornike Gelayevich Kvitiya (; born 17 April 1992) is a Russian football player. ==Club career== He made his debut in the Russian Professional Football League for FC Kolomna on 28 July 2016 in a game against SFC CRFSO Smolensk. ==References== ==Other websites== * Profile by Russian Professional Football League Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers
